General Information

Blended with our pure RosehipPLUS Rosehip Oil, this Daily Cream Cleanser gently lifts away make-up and impurities. Containing Jojoba and Sea Buckthorn, it helps to maintain the skins perfect moisture balance for optimum comfort and radiance

Directions

Apply morning and night with gentle circular movements over face and neck and simply rinse with warm water or remove with a cotton pad to dissolve the day's pollutants without irritating the skin, leaving it feeling soft and perfectly refreshed.
